      • retrieve

        public static int retrieve​(cp213.BST<java.lang.Character> tree,
                           java.io.File file)
                    throws java.io.FileNotFoundException
        Determine the number of comparisons to retrieve the contents of a file from a tree. Reset the number of comparisons, then attempt to retrieve every letter in the file from tree. All letters must be converted to upper case.
        Parameters:
        tree - The BST to process.
        file - The file to process.
        Returns:
        The number of comparisons necessary to find every letter in file in tree.
        Throws:
        java.io.FileNotFoundException - Thrown if file not found.

        Train a tree by inserting all letters from a file into the tree. Letters must be converted to upper-case. Non-letters are ignored.
        Parameters:

        file - The file to read into the tree.
        Throws:
